description: Service Bus MQ Manager works by monitoring a Queue and parsing the Messages presenting them in a list sorted by Commands, Events, Messages and Errors. Currently MSMQ and Azure Service Bus queues are supported, and message parsing for MassTransit and NServiceBus is supported, its also possible to create a new Service Bus Adapter for other Service Bus messages and Queue providers.
summary: Service Bus MQ Manager works by monitoring a Queue and parsing the Messages presenting them in a list sorted by Commands, Events, Messages and Errors.
